      <title>将耗油大车换成电动车是否具有经济意义？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ev-costs-are-rising-are-they-better-value-than-gas-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直到最近，购买电动汽车对于世界各地的许多人来说都是有意义的，不仅仅是出于环境原因，而且还有经济原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ev-costs-are-rising-are-they-better-value-than-gas-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:38:51 GMT</pubDate>
