    <item>
      <title>卡森·布洛克 (Carson Block) 的抵押贷款房地产投资信托基金 (REIT) 痛苦预测开始成真</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/carson-block-s-call-for-blackstone-reit-stress-starts-to-show-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石抵押信托公司 (Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc.) 将股息削减 24% 的举措开始为卖空者卡森·布洛克 (Carson Block) 带来胜利，布洛克认为黑石抵押信托公司可能受到商业地产危机的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/carson-block-s-call-for-blackstone-reit-stress-starts-to-show-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超级富豪以外的所有人的房地产市场都崩溃了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/real-estate-market-is-broken-for-everyone-except-the-ultra-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国是几十年来最难负担的房地产市场之一，住宅销售陷入停滞，一代有志于购房的人被拒之门外。但有一个群体却对这场危机泰然处之：富人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/real-estate-market-is-broken-for-everyone-except-the-ultra-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:32:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
